<h2>Your Order Has Shipped! 🚚</h2>

<p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

<p>Great news! Your order <strong>#{{orderNumber}}</strong> has been shipped by <strong>{{sellerName}}</strong>.</p>

<div class="success-box">
  <div class="summary-row"><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> {{#if trackingNumber}}{{trackingNumber}}{{else}}N/A{{/if}}</div>
  <div class="summary-row"><strong>Shipping Method:</strong> {{#if shippingMethod}}{{shippingMethod}}{{else}}Standard Delivery{{/if}}</div>
  <div class="summary-row"><strong>Estimated Delivery:</strong> {{#if estimatedDelivery}}{{estimatedDelivery}}{{else}}2–5 business days{{/if}}</div>
</div>

<h3>Items Shipped:</h3>
<table class="order-table">
  {{#each items}}
  <tr>
    <td>
      <strong>{{this.name}}</strong>
    </td>
    <td style="text-align: right;">
      Qty: {{this.quantity}}
    </td>
  </tr>
  {{/each}}
</table>

{{#if trackingUrl}}
<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="btn btn-green">Track Shipment</a>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{platformUrl}}/orders" class="btn">View Order Details</a>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions about your delivery, contact the seller or our support team.</p>
